Package org.openwms.common.transport.commands

Class TransportUnitCommandHandler

java.lang.Object
org.openwms.common.transport.commands.TransportUnitCommandHandler
@Validated @TxService class TransportUnitCommandHandler extends Object
A TransportUnitCommandHandler is just a handler or an adapter implementation that is used by a listener and passes incoming TUCommands to the internal ApplicationContext.
Author:
Heiko Scherrer
